                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Koob, G. F. & Volkow, N. D.</span>: <span class="ti">Neurocircuitry of addiction.</span> <span class='so'>Neuropsychopharmacology, 35, 217-238 (2010)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19710631" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Kenny, P. J.</span>: <span class="ti">Epigenetics, microRNA, and addiction.</span> <span class='so'>Dialogues Clin. Neurosci., 16, 335-344 (2014)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25364284" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Nestler, E. J.</span>: <span class="ti">Epigenetic mechanisms of drug addiction.</span> <span class='so'>Neuropharmacology, 76 Pt B, 259-268 (2014)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23643695" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Renthal, W., Kumar, A., Xiao, G. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Genome-wide analysis of chromatin regulation by cocaine reveals a role for sirtuins.</span> <span class='so'>Neuron, 62, 335-348 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19447090" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Renthal, W., Maze, I., Krishnan, V. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Histone deacetylase 5 epigenetically controls behavioral adaptations to chronic emotional stimuli.</span> <span class='so'>Neuron, 56, 517-529 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17988634" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Taniguchi, M., Carreira, M. B., Smith, L. N. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Histone deacetylase 5 limits cocaine reward through cAMP-induced nuclear import.</span> <span class='so'>Neuron, 73, 108-120 (2012)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22243750" target="_blank">PubMed</a>] [<a href="http://first.lifesciencedb.jp/archives/4424" target="_blank">新着論文レビュー</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R7"><span class=